Unity Localization StringTable files are created on PC #2 via
Window > Asset Management > Localization Tables.

Required tables:
  Table Collection: "Game"
  Locales: uk (Ukrainian, default), en (English)

Key list (add to both locales):
  lobby.waiting
  lobby.connected
  lobby.session_unavailable
  map_select.choose
  map_select.waiting_opponent
  setup.waiting_opponent
  game.your_turn
  game.opponent_turn
  result.victory
  result.defeat
  result.draw
